..
../
../../
../../../
../**
../../**
../../../**

## Exclude node modules and test artifacts - must be first and absolute
node_modules
**/node_modules
.vscode/
.vscode-test/
.vscode-test-web/
**/__tests__/**
**/*.spec.*
**/*.test.*
e2e/
test/

## Build and editor files
## Keep the built extension entrypoint but exclude sourcemaps and other large build artifacts
dist/**/*.map
dist/**/*.d.ts
build/
coverage/
*.map

## Git and CI - exclude completely
.git
.git/**
.github/
**/.git
**/.git/**

## Root-level ignores that may be pulled in from monorepo
../../.eslintignore
../../.gitignore
../../.npmignore
../../.prettierignore

## Large or irrelevant folders
**/playwright-report/**
**/test-results/**
**/node_modules/**
node_modules/.bin/**
**/.bin/**

## VSCE doesn't allow packaging files outside the extension folder; explicitly
## exclude any paths that reference parent directories to prevent invalid
## relative paths being added to the package file list.
**/..*/**
